resources.string: "L-ID tat-tagħmir mhux tajba: %s L-ID tat-tagħmir għandha tkun numru IMEI jew indirizz MAC tajjeb. Mingħajr l-ID tat-tagħmir, ċerti faċilitajiet tal-Mi Kont u x-Xiaomi Cloud mhux se jkunu disponibbli."
To turn on %s, Xiaomi Service Framework will send SMS to verify your phone number. You will be charged for the regular SMS by the carrier.
